reviewText: This two-parter is probably the best episode of the last season. The original Ray returns as the show explains his disappearance.Platinum Disc Corp has made an excellent DVD on this title, complete with surround sound.  This is surprising as Platinum generally only does Public Domain titles (which they do a very good job with).I only gave it 4 stars because there are no extras, alternate languages, or subtitles.This is now available in the Canadian Season 4 set, so you may not want to duplicate your purchases.
summary: The best episode of the last season!
